{"tid":1853960,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"香港人如何自救？ - 馮睎乾","createTime":"2020-01-31T09:11:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T09:44:06.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"53adda79f7aa10786b8b7b539a0de8039406d49a","tid":1853960,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T09:11:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%A6%AE%E7%9D%8E%E4%B9%BE/daily/article/20200131/20853208/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25A6%25AE%25E7%259D%258E%25E4%25B9%25BE%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200131%2F20853208%2F&d=7U4Tv3rjd6zAHDU%2B6Dwik34HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=17f98ee1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25A6%25AE%25E7%259D%258E%25E4%25B9%25BE%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200131%2F20853208%2F&h=b9925510\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%A6%AE%E7%9D%8E%E4%B9%BE/daily/article/20200131/20853208/</a><br />\n<br />\n香港人如何自救？ - 馮睎乾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200131/large/1580376130_9406.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200131%2Flarge%2F1580376130_9406.jpg&h=32a0a654&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n沒比較就沒傷害，在賀一誠面前，鄭月娥固然連一坨屎也不是，但原來連董建華也不失禮，當年full gear勇闖牛頭角下邨的董太，我們更欠她一個交代。現在有政府等於無政府，不，衰過無政府，有理由懷疑：香港鬧口罩荒，是由於特區政府在全球瘋狂搶貨，導致市民網購也有困難。搶貨用意何在，無法查證，但按我上週寫的「這是肺炎版721」劇本，則是司馬昭之心了。<br />\n<br />\n香港人只能自救，但怎麼救呢？其實是常識題。假如你是大宅主人，發現管家與匪類勾結，前門放火後門放賊，把你的金銀珠寶、柴米油鹽，統統送到賊人手中，現在還想下毒殺你全家，怎辦？從前心智正常的人，定然二話不說手起刀落，先把她剁成肉醬再說。現代人奉公守法，當然不能這樣暴力，但至少也得攆走她，替自己止止血。無奈管家婆已安排三十大盜做護衛員，你趕不走她，如何是好？生死攸關，自然走為上策。<br />\n<br />\n逃跑不但不可恥，簡直超有用，在古人此乃常識，奇怪現代人好像喪失了這種直覺。當然，逃跑價值高低，視乎你是什麼人，中西之異亦可見於此：東漢桓景聽從仙人指引，九月九日登高避災，喝菊花酒，之後中國就有了重陽節；一六六五年倫敦爆發黑死病，牛頓回鄉避疫，潛研學問，人間就有了微積分和萬有引力定律。重陽節和萬有引力，分別代表中西方對人類文明的貢獻&mdash;&mdash;重陽是假期，自然重要得多。<br />\n<br />\n理智告訴你要走，但你也未必捨得，尤其是誓死留港的黃絲。至於愛國藍絲，離開這個被暴徒蹂躪的地方，應該沒什心理關口吧？根據大陸官方公佈的權威數據，截至一月廿九日中午，大灣區多地的疫情都比香港輕，我誠意向愛國藍推介三大避疫勝地：第二、三位是河源、汕尾，兩市人口超過三百萬，但只有一宗武漢肺炎；第一位是江門，四百五十萬人口，也是一宗。<br />\n<br />\n希望藍絲們可廣傳以下正能量訊息：「信任主席，北上避疫！河源汕尾，防毒有力！最強醫護，江門出色！住得舒適，食得招積，齊返大陸，死得超值！」 <br />\n<br />\n馮睎乾<br />\n電郵 :philomusus@gmail.com"},{"pid":"e9d36881e1ce71a1adef8c5821f287082c9db2b3","tid":1853960,"uid":281652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T09:13:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aaa514d99181f81f65005a90adfbd3bcb3d7e0a","tid":1853960,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9d36881e1ce71a1adef8c5821f287082c9db2b3","tid":1853960,"uid":281652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T09:13:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T09:26:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32bd3b2955f3be3cfb7a09a9fc7badaba0ae66d2","tid":1853960,"uid":172668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T09:35:32.000Z","msg":"支持藍絲死返去大灣區<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b0b44f0642d86de7afa2484306da117e94b29f6","tid":1853960,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T09:37:42.000Z","msg":"「信任主席，北上避疫！河源汕尾，防毒有力！最強醫護，江門出色！住得舒適，食得招積，齊返大陸，死得超值！」<br />\n<br />\n大家知唔知呢段係改編自邊度 ？<br />\n<br />\n利申 ： 我知"},{"pid":"12c58d08f4349beb3699f6b7cd0e357c7b0ad715","tid":1853960,"uid":292987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T09:44:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}